Title: First In person Fundraiser Since the Pandemic for the President
Narrative:
‌Mainstream politics and events returns in US as Joe Biden holds his first in-person Fundraiser in Washington since the Pandemic. 

Although Biden as attend certain meetings the return to fundraisers give hopes of slow restoration of normal years.

‌According to Associate press at least 3million dollars had been raised for the Democratic National Commitee.
‌
‌To a group of 18 donors present and 4 virtual donors Biden talked on the topics such as inflation, Russian invasion on Ukraine causing oil markets to crash and climate change.
‌
‌It is a crucial time for Democrats as they have to be financially secure before going to the polls. During the pandemic too many of the Democrats raised fund online.Since Covid -19 is at a state of declining it would be a tight schedule for Biden travelling and raising funds for the party. 
‌
‌Source: Association of Press
